name: Agent Break Logs
query:
SELECT
    BL.name as "Applied Break:Link/Break Log:150",
    A.agent_name as "Agent:Link/Agent:180",
    BL.break_type as "Type",
    DATE(BL.start_time) as "Start::140",
    DATE(BL.end_time) as "End::140",
    TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, BL.start_time, BL.end_time) as "Duration"
    
FROM
    `tabBreak Log` BL
JOIN
    `tabAgent` A ON A.name = BL.agent;
